#~ "</p><p>Default: all\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "</p><p><b><big>callback</big> = \"</b><i>/path/to/callback</i><b>\"</b>\n"
#~ "</p><p>If this directive is defined, <b>ldirectord</b> automatically "
